For agents that support Copilot CLI's project-local skills under `.github/skills/`:

- `deploying-demo` — Full deployment workflow (prerequisites, azd up, SRE Agent config, verification)
- `running-demo` — Break/fix scenarios with browser verification
- `managing-sre-agent` — Create/manage SRE Agent skills, response plans, knowledge files

